{"tid":156471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"廠迷眾籌準備「空襲」雲加","createTime":"2017-03-14T18:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T12:16:16.000Z","uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64964e439554c49c1a546f8ea34d6edb12dcd856","tid":156471,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c88bc754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】部份阿仙奴球迷於網上集資超過2000鎊，並準備以飛機在酋長球場上空，展示要求領隊雲加離任的橫額。<br />\n<br />\n雖然阿仙奴剛躋身英格蘭足總盃最後4強，不少廠迷均對領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）今季以來的領軍成績有微言，尤其球隊於英超積分榜跌出前4位，更在歐聯16強以2:10的總比數，被拜仁慕尼黑淘汰出局。<br />\n<br />\n有阿仙奴粉絲希望效法曼聯球迷此前藉飛機展示要求前領隊莫耶斯離開的橫額，並於網上設立眾籌網站，而現時已有115位廠迷響應，並籌得2,265鎊，距離3,000鎊的空中飄揚橫額實際費用，已經不遠。<br />\n<br />\n該個集資網站的聲明指出：「我們籌款為了向阿仙奴班主們轉達撤換雲加的想法，他不斷帶來難令人滿足的成績，而忠心的阿仙奴球迷已經受夠。」"},{"pid":"5548c577e9eeb6f9958daf13080a9c149c6d725f","tid":156471,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"成班無血性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1151c0edd373f972e74573c4b34509007a344514","tid":156471,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"好學唔學，學獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c57579cbb9b8f397787d1c615b77383b5b69f6","tid":156471,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49d3e8f71349549538f7bea91bd0b316ef0fab3","tid":156471,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好學唔學，學獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=